element.name: Mini Sugarloaf by moyle, Traditional Cache (1/2)
element.description: Walk for about 10 to 20 mins along the forest path - keeping to the left. It is only at the last stretch that the terrain get tough!
element.long-description: Additional Waypoints HH15DAN - Mini Sugarloaf N 53째 12.307 W 006째 17.545 This is a good place to park.
element.encoded-hints: This cache gets it's name from the view.

ul.li:
2010-05-22T19:00:00Z : Found it by wilf28
Great place for a cache - found it with Stern29 on a pleasant day.
TFTC

2010-05-22T19:00:00Z : Found it by Stern29
What a great view. Thanks for showing. To bad that there was not enought time to rest at the water after all.
But the cache needs maintenance immediately. The lid is broken and there was a slug (not a TB slug [;)] inside. Greetings from Germany and TFTC anyhow

2010-02-16T20:00:00Z : Found it by redflame1
Found on a lovely sunny afternoon after Glencree Cache [^]
Nice views from the top!
In: Angel Badge Out: Aloha TB
TFTC! [:D]

2010-01-30T20:00:00Z : Found it by enidan1981
Found it today together with DoJoPa on a bright and sunny day (with a little bit of sun burn :o) Dropped Aloha Bug Needs maintenance urgently! TFTC

2010-01-30T20:00:00Z : Found it by DoJoPa
The first in a row of our cache tour trough the Wicklow Mountains today. Found it on a sunny winter day ... great view! TFTC!
